{{vgname|质量效应 传奇版|en=Mass Effect Legendary Edition}}是[[电子游戏|电子游戏]][[质量效应系列|质量效应]]三部曲《[[质量效应_(游戏)|质量效应]]》、《[[质量效应2|质量效应2]]》和《[[质量效应3|质量效应3]]》的合集，由[[BioWare|BioWare]]开发，[[艺电|艺电]]发行。三款游戏都进行了[[數位修復|复刻]]，包括视觉效果增强、技术改进和玩法调整，其中三部曲第一部进行了更大范围的升级，特别是在画面、战斗机制、车辆操控和加载时间方面。

《传奇版》的开发工作于2019年开始，由马克·沃尔特斯监制，他曾担任过《质量效应2》和《质量效应3》的首席编剧。为保留三部曲原汁原味的体验，BioWare决定将该项目作为复刻版而非重制版来开发。合集于2020年11月7日公布，2021年5月14日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]平台发行，无官方中文。《传奇版》获得了业界相当积极的评价，第一部游戏的增强体验以及合集的便利与广度受到赞扬，而某些方面玩法和视觉变化的程度受到略微批评。

==内容==
[[File:MassEffect1_LegendaryEdition_Combat.png|300px]]》与续作相比获得了更广泛的升级，包括新的[[平视显示器_(电子游戏)|HUD]]。<ref name="GIReview" />]]
《质量效应 传奇版》包含原版三部曲《[[质量效应_(游戏)|质量效应]]》（2007）、《[[质量效应2|质量效应2]]》（2010）和《[[质量效应3|质量效应3]]》（2012）中的所有单人基础内容<ref name="announcement">{{cite web |last1=Hudson |first1=Casey |title=Happy N7 Day! |url=https://blog.bioware.com/2020/11/07/happy-n7-day-4/ |website=BioWare Blog |access-date=2021-01-15 |date=2020-11-07 |dead-url=no |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20201107211703/https://blog.bioware.com/2020/11/07/happy-n7-day-4/ }}</ref>，以及最初游戏发布的几乎所有单人[[可下载内容|可下载内容]]（DLC），如促销武器、盔甲和扩展包{{efn|《传奇版》不包含《[[质量效应_(游戏)|质量效应]]》中的《巅峰基地》（''Pinnacle Station''）扩展包。<ref name="pinnacle station">{{cite web |last1=Ruppert |first1=Liana |title=BioWare Explains Pinnacle Station DLC Exclusion From Mass Effect Legendary Edition, "Heartbreaking" |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-pinnacle-station-dlc-exclusion-from-mass-effect-legendary-edition |website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207013235/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-pinnacle-station-dlc-exclusion-from-mass-effect-legendary-edition |archive-date=2021-02-07 |date=2021-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}。三部曲的背景设定在22世纪的[[银河系|银河系]]，玩家扮演一名精锐的人类士兵{{le|薛帕德指挥官|Commander Shepard}}，他/她必须团结银河系，共同对抗被称为“收割者”的高度先进的合成有机星舰种族<ref name="abstraction">{{cite web |title=Mass Effect - Abstraction |url=https://abstraction.games/project/mass-effect-legendary-edition |website=Abstraction Games Official Website |access-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210115215858/https://abstraction.games/project/mass-effect-legendary-edition |archive-date=2021-01-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。薛帕德是一个可定制角色，其性别、外貌、军事背景、战斗训练和名字均由玩家决定<ref>{{cite web |last1=Perez |first1=Diego |title=Mass Effect Character Creation Guide: Best Pre-Service History, Psychological Profile, and Class |url=https://attackofthefanboy.com/guides/mass-effect-character-creation-guide-best-pre-service-history-psychological-profile-and-class/ |website=Attack of the Fanboy |access-date=2021-09-26 |archive-url=https://archive.today/o3GSq |archive-date=2021-09-26 |date=2021-05-15 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在每一作游戏中，玩家做出的选择会以各种方式影响故事发展，这些选择和后果贯穿了整个三部曲<ref name="eurogamer">{{cite web |author1=Eurogamer Staff |title=The games we're looking forward to in 2021 |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-01-08-the-games-were-looking-forward-to-in-2021 |website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |access-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210115220231/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-01-08-the-games-were-looking-forward-to-in-2021 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |date=2021-01-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《传奇版》中的三款游戏都进行了[[數位修復|复刻]]，包括[[材质贴图|纹理]]、[[着色器|着色器]]、模型、特效和技术特性更新。与原作相比，复刻版均以更清晰的分辨率和更高的[[帧率|帧率]]运行<ref name="announcement" />。玩家可从合集中的统一启动器启动三款游戏，另外还有一个包括三款游戏定制选项的通用[[创建角色|角色创建器]]。之前在前几代游戏中不可用的《质量效应3》默认的女性薛帕德指挥官模型，现在可在整个三部曲中使用。第二部和第三部游戏的玩法与原版相似，但也得到了一些调整，比如《质量效应3》中的“银河备战”（Galactic Readiness）系统进行了再平衡，以弥补缺失[[多人电子游戏|多人模式]]带来的影响<ref name="gamespot changes">{{cite web |last1=James |first1=Lucy |last2=Ramée |first2=Jordan |title=What Mass Effect: Legendary Edition Is Changing About The Original Trilogy |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-mass-effect-legendary-edition-is-changing-about-the-original-trilogy/1100-6486987/ |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |access-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210206204423/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-mass-effect-legendary-edition-is-changing-about-the-original-trilogy/1100-6486987/ |archive-date=2021-02-06 |date=2021-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每作游戏还新添加了[[游戏内摄影|照片模式]]，玩家可在游戏中调整并捕捉屏幕[[截图|截图]]<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Chalk |first1=Andy |title=Mass Effect: Legendary Edition has a photo mode and it looks pretty sweet |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-has-a-photo-mode-and-it-looks-pretty-sweet/ |magazine=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |access-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210417163156/https://www.pcgamer.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-has-a-photo-mode-and-it-looks-pretty-sweet/ |archive-date=2021-04-17 |date=2021-04-16 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

三部曲第一部则进行了更广泛的升级<ref name="PCG">{{cite web |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/in-mass-effect-legendary-edition-the-first-game-is-a-partial-remake-the-sequels-are-remasters/ |title=In Mass Effect: Legendary Edition the first game is a partial remake, the sequels are remasters |first=Rich |last=Stanton |date=2021-02-02 |access-date=2021-02-02 |magazine=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207164205/https://www.pcgamer.com/in-mass-effect-legendary-edition-the-first-game-is-a-partial-remake-the-sequels-are-remasters/ |archive-date=2021-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏包括额外的视觉更新，例如在某些关卡中加入了烟雾效果和[[体积光|体积光]]，以及天空盒（Skybox）的改进。战斗系统也进行了更新以更贴近续作，包括射击瞄准、近战按钮、武器平衡以及[[人工智能|人工智能]]等的改进<ref name="gamespot changes" /> 。某些[[頭目_(角色類型)|Boss]]遭遇也进行了调整，通过扩大[[關卡_(電子遊戲)|关卡布局]]和更频繁地自动[[游戏存档|保存]]来减少玩家挫败感<ref name="bosses">{{cite web |last1=Ruppert |first1=Liana |title=How Mass Effect Legendary Edition Makes Boss Fights More Effective |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/15/how-mass-effect-legendary-edition-makes-boss-fights-more-effective |website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430095928/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/15/how-mass-effect-legendary-edition-makes-boss-fights-more-effective |archive-date=2021-04-30 |date=2021-02-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。玩家使用的全地形车灰鲭鲨号（Mako）也进行了速度提升和操控优化<ref name="gimako">{{cite web |last1=Ruppert |first1=Liana |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition Mako Changes, What's Different |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/mass-effect-legendary-edition-mako-changes-whats-different |website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207163658/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/mass-effect-legendary-edition-mako-changes-whats-different |archive-date=2021-02-07 |date=2021-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。原始游戏中被普遍诟病的加载时间也进行了调整，玩家在电梯中的等待时间减少，电梯被用作隐藏加载画面的一种方式<ref name="elevators">{{cite web |last1=Ruppert |first1=Liana |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition Changes Iconic Elevator Sequences |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/03/mass-effect-legendary-edition-changes-iconic-elevator-sequences |website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207163157/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/03/mass-effect-legendary-edition-changes-iconic-elevator-sequences |archive-date=2021-02-07 |date=2021-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==开发==
《质量效应 传奇版》由[[BioWare|BioWare]]开发，[[艺电|艺电]]发行<ref>{{cite web |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition |url=https://www.ea.com/games/mass-effect/mass-effect-legendary-edition |website=Mass Effect Legendary Edition Official Website |access-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=http://archive.today/JEfmP|archive-date=2021-02-06 |url-status=live}}</ref>。BioWare曾在2014年讨论开发质量效应三部曲的复刻版<ref name="pcinvasion">{{cite web |author1=PC Invasion |title=Mass Effect 'N7 Day' stream teased, remastered trilogy hints persist |url=https://www.pcinvasion.com/mass-effect-n7-day-stream-teased-remastered-trilogy-hints-persist/ |website=PC Invasion |access-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210115221147/https://www.pcinvasion.com/mass-effect-n7-day-stream-teased-remastered-trilogy-hints-persist/ |archive-date=2021-01-15 |date=2014-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但直到2019年才开始该项目的工作<ref name="eurog date announce">{{cite web |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-02-02-mass-effect-returns-bioware-talks-trilogy-tweaks-and-franchise-revival |title=Mass Effect returns: BioWare talks trilogy tweaks and franchise revival |first=Tom |last=Phillips |date=2021-02-02 |access-date=2021-02-02 |website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210202170147/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-02-02-mass-effect-returns-bioware-talks-trilogy-tweaks-and-franchise-revival |archive-date=2021-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。BioWare签约了多个支持工作室协助其开发，包括Abstraction Games和Blind Squirrel Games<ref name="abstraction" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Our Games |url=https://blindsquirrelentertainment.com/games-3/ |website=Blind Squirrel Games Official Website |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504135235/https://blindsquirrelentertainment.com/games-3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前者协助开发新一代游戏机版本，主要在[[计算机图形|画面]]上进行优化和改进<ref name="abstraction" />。整个项目由马克·沃尔特斯监制，他曾担任《质量效应2》和《质量效应3》的首席编剧<ref name="ign impressions">{{cite web |last1=Bailey |first1=Kat |title=Mass Effect: Legendary Edition First Impressions: Less Than a Remake, but Much More Than a Basic Remaster |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/mass-effect-legendary-edition-first-impressions-less-than-a-remake-but-much-more-than-a-basic-remaster |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210203154633/https://www.ign.com/articles/mass-effect-legendary-edition-first-impressions-less-than-a-remake-but-much-more-than-a-basic-remaster |archive-date=2021-02-03 |date=2021-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在开发早期，BioWare咨询了[[Epic_Games|Epic Games]]将游戏从原来的[[虚幻引擎|虚幻引擎3]][[移植_(軟體)|移植]]到虚幻引擎4的可行性。BioWare最终确定这样做所需的工作量很大，需要重做大部分游戏内容，例如重做所有的[[剧情画面|过场动画]]。他们还担心如此大规模的翻修会从根本上改变和剥夺原版三部曲的体验<ref name="ign impressions" />。所以BioWare决定不升级游戏引擎，同时将该项目作为复刻版而非[[电子游戏重制|重制版]]来开发<ref name="gi remaster remake">{{cite web |last1=Wallace |first1=Kimberley |title=Why Mass Effect Legendary Edition Is A Remaster (Not A Remake) |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/05/why-mass-effect-legendary-edition-is-a-remaster-not-a-remake |website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207190208/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/05/why-mass-effect-legendary-edition-is-a-remaster-not-a-remake |archive-date=2021-02-07 |date=2021-02-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于《质量效应3》多人模式的复杂性和项目时间的限制，BioWare决定不添加这一模式<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-why-it-didnt-bring-back-mass-effect-3-multiplayer-in-legendary-edition |title=BioWare Explains Why It Didn't Bring Back Mass Effect 3 Multiplayer In Legendary Edition |first=Liana |last=Ruppert |magazine=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |date=2021-02-02 |access-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207184054/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-why-it-didnt-bring-back-mass-effect-3-multiplayer-in-legendary-edition |archive-date=2021-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。团队打算将所有单人DLC都包含在合集中，但《质量效应》中的《巅峰基地》由于源代码已损坏而无法添加，沃尔特斯称这“令人心碎”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-pinnacle-station-dlc-exclusion-from-mass-effect-legendary-edition |title=BioWare Explains Pinnacle Station DLC Exclusion From Mass Effect Legendary Edition, "Heartbreaking" |first=Liana |last=Ruppert |date=2021-02-02 |access-date=2021-02-02 |magazine=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207013235/https://www.gameinformer.com/2021/02/02/bioware-explains-pinnacle-station-dlc-exclusion-from-mass-effect-legendary-edition |archive-date=2021-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

作为复刻过程的一部分，BioWare利用人工智能[[图像缩放|放大]]程序和其他定制工具提高了三部曲游戏中所有纹理的分辨率<ref>{{cite web |last1=Grubb |first1=Jeff |title=BioWare used AI upscaling to remaster Mass Effect's original textures |url=https://venturebeat.com/2021/02/02/bioware-used-ai-upscaling-to-remaster-mass-effects-original-textures/ |website=GamesBeat |publisher=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207192032/https://venturebeat.com/2021/02/02/bioware-used-ai-upscaling-to-remaster-mass-effects-original-textures/ |archive-date=2021-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。初步的视觉升级完成后，美术部门开始着手资源、人物模型和环境的制作.<ref>{{cite web |title=Visual Improvements |url=https://www.ea.com/games/mass-effect/mass-effect-legendary-edition/news/visual-improvements |website=Mass Effect Legendary Edition Official Website |publisher=[[Electronic_Arts|Electronic Arts]] |access-date=October 3, 2021 |archive-url=https://archive.today/I04sY |archive-date=October 3, 2021 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在审视了每作游戏的潜在变化后，团队认为女性角色的某些镜头角度不必要或需要改进，因此他们改动了一些原始镜头<ref name="Censorship">{{cite web|title=BioWare 'censors' Mass Effect Legendary Edition butt shots and gamers are mad|url=https://www.gamerevolution.com/features/673736-bioware-censors-mass-effect-legendary-edition|access-date=2021-02-19|date=2021-02-09|last=Tamburro|first=Paul|website=[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210209201028/https://www.gamerevolution.com/features/673736-bioware-censors-mass-effect-legendary-edition|archive-date=2021-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至2020年春，《传奇版》处于完全可玩的“基线”状态，BioWare已实施了第一轮改进。然而，团队认为《质量效应》一代在视觉效果上仍然落后于其他两代，因此请来了游戏的原美术指导德里克·沃茨（Derek Watts）增加新的细节和效果。为了让游戏体验更现代化，消除与续作的差距，一代的复刻版还有大量的玩法更新<ref name="eurog date announce" />，如在一位原关卡设计师的帮助下，游戏调整了最初被玩家视为“痛苦 ”的Boss遭遇战<ref name="bosses" />。合集于2021年4月9日[[軟件版本週期#生产商发放（Release_to_Manufacturing，RTM）|交付发行商]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Gurwin |first1=Gabe |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition Has Gone Gold Ahead Of May 14 Launch |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/mass-effect-legendary-edition-has-gone-gold-ahead-of-may-14-launch/1100-6490007/ |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210410162446/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/mass-effect-legendary-edition-has-gone-gold-ahead-of-may-14-launch/1100-6490007/ |archive-date=2021-04-10 |date=2021-04-10 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

==发行==
《传奇版》于2020年11月7日——一年一度BioWare庆祝质量效应系列的“N7日”——正式公布<ref name="announcement" />。合集于2021年5月14日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]平台发行<ref name="eurog date announce" />。虽然《传奇版》通过[[向下兼容|向下兼容]]模式在[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X]]和[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]上运行并具有针对性的增强，但BioWare没有计划为这些主机平台发布专门的版本<ref>{{cite web |last1=Valentine |first1=Rebekah |title=Why Mass Effect Legendary Edition Won't Come to PS5 and Xbox Series X |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/why-mass-effect-legendary-edition-wont-come-to-ps5-and-xbox-series-x |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2021-02-02 |access-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210207185016/https://www.ign.com/articles/why-mass-effect-legendary-edition-wont-come-to-ps5-and-xbox-series-x |archive-date=2021-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在一次采访中，沃尔特斯表示他个人希望将该合集移植到[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]上，但该游戏机不在项目计划中<ref name="eurog date announce" />。

