根据聚合评论网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的统计，《质量效应 传奇版》 的Microsoft Windows和PlayStation 4版本获得了媒体“正面评论为主”的评价，Xbox One版本获得了“普遍赞誉” <ref name="MCPC" /><ref name="MCPS" /><ref name="MCX" />。

媒体普遍认为，《质量效应》一代在《传奇版》中得到了明显改善，比其两个续作得到了更广泛的升级。[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]的阿利萨·梅尔坎特（Alyssa Mercante）认为，一代的改进使得其体验更现代化，BioWare在保持原作魅力的情况下成功地使一代与续作更加一致<ref name="GR+Review" />。GamingBolt的舒班卡·帕里贾特（Shubhankar Parijat）断言复刻版是他见过的最令人印象深刻的作品之一，他把这归功于对资源、环境、照明和人物模型所做的大量工作<ref name="GamingBolt">{{cite web |last1=Parijat |first1=Shubhankar |title=Mass Effect: Legendary Edition Review – Favourite Trilogy on the Citadel |url=https://gamingbolt.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-review-favourite-trilogy-on-the-citadel |website=GamingBolt |access-date=2021-08-17 |archive-url=https://archive.today/pWdcM |archive-date=2021-08-17 |date=2021-05-18 |url-status=live}}</ref>。 相反，一些评论员认为视觉变化太过头，掩盖了原作的情绪和基调<ref>{{cite web |last1=Donaldson |first1=Alex |title=The Mass Effect Remaster in Legendary Edition is excellent, but showy visuals overshadow some of the original's mood and tone |url=https://www.vg247.com/2021/05/13/mass-effect-remaster-legendary-edition-graphics-lighting/ |website=[[VG247|VG247]] |access-date=2021-05-22 |date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://archive.today/DIKfQ |archive-date=2021-05-29 |url-status=live}}</ref>，而其他评论员则认为游戏玩法的更新还不够深入<ref name="PCGamerReview" />。

《传奇版》中的《质量效应2》和《质量效应3》更新较小，但媒体同样反响积极。[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的埃里克·范·艾伦（Eric Van Allen）赞扬了《传奇版》对《质量效应2》的道德系统所作的调整，认为这使得游戏感觉不那么无情<ref name="DestRev" />。[[IGN|IGN]]的丹·斯特普尔顿（Dan Stapleton）认为，《质量效应2》的画面改进后看起来更现代化，但面部动画是最大弱项<ref name="IGNRev2" />。Push Square的罗伯特·拉姆齐（Robert Ramsey）指出《质量效应3》包含了基础游戏中没有的扩展内容，使游戏体验得到了有意义的提升<ref name="PSReview" />。相比之下，[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的乔丹·拉米（Jordan Ramée）批评该合集没有将DLC很好地整合到单一游戏的整体叙事中<ref name="GSpotReview" />。

作为一个全面的作品，《质量效应 传奇版》因其便捷、广度和对《质量效应》三部曲的保存而受到赞扬。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的贾安·埃尔克（Jhaan Elker）向粉丝和新人推荐了该合集，但认为一些玩家可能仍然喜欢带有[[遊戲模組|模組]]的原始版本<ref>{{cite web |last1=Jhaan |first1=Elker |title=I've already played the trilogy. Should I buy 'Mass Effect Legendary Edition'? |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/video-games/reviews/mass-effect-legendary-edition-review/ |website=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |access-date=2021-05-22 |date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210515010956/https://www.washingtonpost.com/video-games/reviews/mass-effect-legendary-edition-review/ |archive-date=2021-05-15 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在针对游戏的性能评测中，[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的托马斯·摩根（Thomas Morgan）强调合集的抱负与努力，并认为游戏最终是“该系列的一个完美跳跃点”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Morgan |first1=Thomas |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition: PS5, Xbox Series X and Series S tested |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-2021-mass-effect-legendary-edition-tested-on-next-gen-consoles |website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |access-date=2021-05-22 |date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://archive.today/rlhU9 |archive-date=2021-05-29 |url-status=live}}</ref>。[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]的金佰利·华莱士（Kimberly Wallace）从整体角度称赞了《质量效应》三部曲，并对复刻版保持对该系列的关注以及让玩家有机会以最完整的形式轻松体验包括所有DLC在内的故事表示感谢<ref name="GIReview" />。

===销量===
《傳奇版》在發售當週登上英國實體銷售排行冠軍<ref name="Game Rant@210518">{{cite web |last=Thomas |first=Ryan |title=Mass Effect: Legendary Edition Claims Top UK Boxed Sales Spot at Launch |website=Game Rant |url=https://gamerant.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-claims-top-uk-boxed-sales-spot-launch/ |access-date=2021-06-03|date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://archive.today/X4Ti8|archive-date=2021-06-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。《傳奇版》的實體銷量雖然未及《[[惡靈古堡_村莊|惡靈古堡 村莊]]》在首週發行時的一半，但不少遊戲評論員預料它在數碼銷售方面會有出色表現<ref name="Game Rant@210518"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-05-17-ps5-stock-influx-boosts-spider-man-miles-morales-sales-uk-boxed-charts |title = PS5 stock influx boosts Spider-Man: Miles Morales sales |last = Dring |first = Christopher |date = 2021-05-17 |publisher = GamesIndustry.biz |language = en |accessdate = 2021-12-31 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20211023012631/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-05-17-ps5-stock-influx-boosts-spider-man-miles-morales-sales-uk-boxed-charts |archivedate = 2021-10-23}}</ref>。在发布一周内，游戏的PC版在[[Steam|Steam]]上的同时在线玩家数超过59,000，为迄今为止BioWare游戏作品中最高<ref>{{cite web |title=Mass Effect Legendary Edition PC has Highest Steam Concurrent Player Count To Date For a Bioware Title |url=https://wccftech.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-pc-highest-concurrent-player-count/ |website=Wccftech |access-date=2021-06-03 |date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210621231508/https://wccftech.com/mass-effect-legendary-edition-pc-highest-concurrent-player-count/ |archive-date=2021-06-21 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在PlayStation商店，《传奇版》2021年5月在美国是销量第三高的游戏，在欧洲是销量第六高的游戏<ref>{{cite web |last1=Massongill |first1=Justin |title=PlayStation Store: May 2021’s Top Downloads |url=https://blog.playstation.com/2021/06/08/playstation-store-may-2021s-top-downloads/ |publisher=[[PlayStation|PlayStation]] |access-date=2021-09-26 |archive-url=https://archive.today/SB7Ex |archive-date=2021-09-26 |date=2021-06-08 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在2021年8月4日的投资者电话会议上，艺电首席执行官安德鲁·威尔逊（Andrew Wilson）透露，游戏的表现“远超”预期，但未披露确切的销售数据<ref>{{cite web |last1=Grubb |first1=Jeff |title=Mass Effect: Legendary Edition outperformed expectations |url=https://venturebeat.com/2021/08/04/mass-effect-legendary-edition-outperformed-expectations/ |website=[[VentureBeat|GamesBeat]] |publisher=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] |access-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://archive.today/Nqii2 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |date=2021-08-04 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

